          <title>New videos show Alex Pretti scuffle with federal officers in Minneapolis 11 days before his death</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Videos that emerged Wednesday show Alex Pretti was forcefully taken to the ground by federal immigration agents after kicking out the tail light of their vehicle during a Minneapolis protest 11 days before he was shot and killed by Border Patrol officers.]]></description>
